    "canonical_statement": "The DAANSphere is interpreted as the base space $S^2$ of a fiber bundle",
    "technical_interpretation": "The DAANSphere is interpreted as the base space $S^2$ of a fiber bundle \\[ T \\longrightarrow E \\longrightarrow S^2, \\] where the fiber over each point is a projection of the same torus \\[ T = S^1 \\times S^1. \\] Formally, the total space $E$ encodes the addressable states so that the local toroidal fibers are mutually isomorphic, $T_i \\cong T_j \\cong T$ for all sampled addresses."
  },
